#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:2 b52f792a421041dd9749521da6fbd4ec
msgid "The TCP Server APIs"
msgstr "TCP 伺服器 API"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:5 207e3afc4b174d23b57784051252cd1a
msgid "TCP Server setup API"
msgstr "TCP 伺服器設定 API"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:7 4b55c6a95a914e4b8125d0261e3e9ee1
msgid ""
"The TCP Server Setup API is used to create a TCP server. The server in the "
"protocol is usually used to connect and listen to the TCP clients and handle"
" the data from the clients."
msgstr "TCP 伺服器設定 API 用於建立 TCP 伺服器。協定中的伺服器通常用於連接和監聽TCP客戶端並處理來自客戶端的資料。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:29 bc025698b381404ab2b38255e6c9a378
msgid ""
"The TCP Server Setup API is defined in the ``TCP_Server_Base`` class. The "
"parameters of the ``__init__`` method are as follows:"
msgstr "TCP 伺服器設定 API 在「TCP_Server_Base」類別中定義。 ``__init__``方法的參數如下："

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:32 3fea17ba735b400ead6845660925c629
msgid "``host``: The host IP address to bind the TCP server to."
msgstr "``host``：綁定 TCP 伺服器的主機 IP 位址。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:33 138fba525e3d4cc4b45de13d41dcccc8
msgid "``port``: The port number to bind the TCP server to."
msgstr "``port``：綁定 TCP 伺服器的連接埠號碼。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:34 5d43377499e340799441608d4b8141ed
msgid ""
"``max_clients``: The maximum number of concurrent clients the server can "
"handle."
msgstr "``max_clients``：伺服器可以處理的並發客戶端的最大數量。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:35 c38a7e31478d4959b7ca63b19d8a9058
msgid "``port_add_step``: The step size for incrementing the port number."
msgstr "``port_add_step``：增加連接埠號碼的步長。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:36 6811a4baaf8d4e8286f8c3e91921a73f
msgid "``port_range_num``: The number of ports to check in the range."
msgstr "``port_range_num``：範圍內要檢查的連接埠數。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:37 8faa3404fac041db9edc663744618cfd
msgid ""
"``max_file_transfer_thread_num``: The maximum number of threads for file "
"transfer operations."
msgstr "``max_file_transfer_thread_num``：檔案傳輸操作的最大執行緒數。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:38 dacdadbcffa2491ca3ef7b17086d1fe7
msgid ""
"``is_hand_alloc_port``: A flag indicating whether to manually allocate the "
"port."
msgstr "``is_hand_alloc_port``：指示是否手動分配連接埠的標誌。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:39 19d4f0e1e91e4e8a88fd29dd6d4029c4
msgid ""
"``is_input_command_in_console``: A flag indicating whether to input commands"
" in the console."
msgstr "``is_input_command_in_console``：指示是否在控制台中輸入指令的標誌。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:40 94c750b6d452441ea4ccaa1b972b3cd6
msgid "``max_custom_workers``: The maximum number of custom worker threads."
msgstr "``max_custom_workers``：自訂工作執行緒的最大數量。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:42 8658c4f5af2f4960865a233821bf2fb6
msgid "All parameters have default values:"
msgstr "每個參數都有預設值："

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:44 b4b329e993944d9d8122d12b33b73324
msgid "``host``: Default is ``'127.0.0.1'``"
msgstr "“主機”：預設為“127.0.0.1”"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:45 666f7dab5e4a40ac8d3c751524db2b86
msgid "``port``: Default is ``65432``"
msgstr "“連接埠”：預設為“65432”"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:46 3b98135aa3ab4c0984ee844a7a263a11
msgid "``max_clients``: Default is ``10``"
msgstr "“max_clients”：預設為“10”"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:47 0d69de2576a94317b91bfb78b84e9c37
msgid "``port_add_step``: Default is ``1``"
msgstr "“port_add_step”：預設為“1”"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:48 e29bb04c24e34a1ea6c02e6faee99584
msgid "``port_range_num``: Default is ``100``"
msgstr "“port_range_num”：預設為“100”"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:49 c02189aa1c8e426287fe8d88d648ff94
msgid "``max_file_transfer_thread_num``: Default is ``10``"
msgstr "“max_file_transfer_thread_num”：預設為“10”"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:50 9932eb5d63f944c9b849bf2dee784ded
msgid "``is_hand_alloc_port``: Default is ``False``"
msgstr "“is_hand_alloc_port”：預設為“False”"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:51 81528c16c70543a7ad10852e80a6f13d
msgid "``is_input_command_in_console``: Default is ``True``"
msgstr "“is_input_command_in_console”：預設為“True”"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:52 578be04f88374e2a973044e2dc61f7cb
msgid "``max_custom_workers``: Default is ``10``"
msgstr "“max_custom_workers”：預設為“10”"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:53 acaba660fce8404c84684d0e36d8cb7d
msgid ""
"``is_extend_command``: Default is ``False`` (when ``True``, ``__init__`` "
"will not call ``start_TCP_Server()`` automatically)"
msgstr ""
"“is_extend_command”：預設為“False”（當“True”時，“__init__”不會自動呼叫“start_TCP_Server()”）"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:56 5ad538fcf7a047cb83c06430fc17868b
msgid ""
"The TCP Server Setup API will initialize all the necessary parameters and "
"resources for the TCP server."
msgstr "TCP 伺服器設定 API 將初始化 TCP 伺服器的所有必要參數和資源。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:59 12ea6aec06374e609665bec9743d0c2d
msgid ""
"*Note: By default ``TCP_Server_Base.__init__`` calls ``start_TCP_Server()`` "
"to start the server automatically. If you set ``is_extend_command=True``, "
"the instance will not auto-start and you should call ``start_TCP_Server()`` "
"manually when ready.*"
msgstr ""
"*注意：預設情況下``TCP_Server_Base.__init__`` 呼叫``start_TCP_Server()`` "
"自動啟動伺服器。如果您設定“is_extend_command=True”，實例將不會自動啟動，您應該在準備好時手動呼叫“start_TCP_Server()”。"
" *"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:70 4cb1d5f3304546ce882398fb5c0036ec
msgid ""
"In the `start_TCP_Server` method, we first create a TCP server socket and "
"bind it to the ``self.host`` and ``self.port`` which are initialized in the "
"``__init__`` method."
msgstr ""
"在`start_TCP_Server`方法中，我們先建立一個TCP伺服器套接字並將其綁定到在`__init__`方法中初始化的`self.host`和`self.port`。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:74 6368d16aba2f4d86abe7e07314a8c506
msgid ""
"*Note: The server socket which is set up in the `start_TCP_Server` method is"
" based on IPv4 form.*"
msgstr "*注意：`start_TCP_Server`方法中設定的伺服器套接字是基於IPv4形式的。 *"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:77 9ae5345fad7a4ae89537ed31b57bd7c1
msgid ""
"Secondly, according to the ``self.is_input_command_in_console`` parameter, "
"we will start a thread to listen to the console input of the server or not."
msgstr ""
"其次，根據``self.is_input_command_in_console``參數，我們會啟動一個執行緒來監聽或不監聽伺服器的控制台輸入。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:81 94e4ccbf323d4134b5297f8c0334ff36
msgid "After that, a main loop to accept clients will be started."
msgstr "之後，將啟動接受客戶端的主循環。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:83 9416322bf1b64db09658b78f87467976
msgid ""
"*Note: there is another global variable ``self.running`` which is set to "
"``True`` after the server socket is successfully created. The "
"``self.running`` variable is used to control the main loop of the TCP "
"server, and it will be set to ``False`` when the server is shutting "
"down.*"
msgstr ""
"*注意：還有另一個全域變數“self.running”，在伺服器套接字成功建立後，該變數將變為“True”。 ``self.running`` "
"變數用於控制 TCP 伺服器的主循環，當伺服器關閉時它將變為 ``False``。 *"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:89 ae36a0bbc490438694c73f02a82e9b31
msgid ""
"The main loop of the TCP setup server function will first checks whether the "
"number of the clients which are connected to the server is over the max "
"clients number or not. By the way, the max clients number limit is defined "
"by the args of the `TCP_Server_Base` class, the ``self.max_clients`` "
"variable which is initialized in the class."
msgstr ""
"TCP建立伺服器函數的主循環首先判斷連接到伺服器的客戶端數量是否超過最大客戶端數量。順便說一句，最大客戶端數量限制是由「TCP_Server_Base」類別的參數定義的，即在類別中初始化的「self.max_clients」變數。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:96 610f3d8802a54760b65ada6338002dd5
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"If the number of the clients is already over the limit of the connect "
"number, the server will send an overload message and close the connection. "
"But if it does not exceed the limit, the server will setup a clients "
"handlers function `handle_client` and the server handler function is defined"
" as:"
msgstr ""
"如果客戶端數量已經超過連線數量限制，伺服器將發送過載訊息並關閉連線。但如果沒有超過限制，伺服器將設定一個客戶端處理函數“handle_client”，伺服器處理函數定義為："

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:108 cb6a4d4fc9ba4dda90a5763a7364dbc9
msgid ""
"*Note: For more details of the `handle_client` function, see the :ref:`tcp-"
"server-handling-information-api` section.*"
msgstr ""
"*注意：有關“handle_client”函數的更多詳細信息，請參閱 :ref:`tcp-server-handling-information-"
"api` 部分。 *"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:111 4d09d17dc1d84ddf903333007e3b65fc
msgid "So what can the setup function do if it fails?"
msgstr "那如果setup函式運行失敗了怎麼辦呢？"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:113 9abaea6541664937a99ee14811cdf79c
msgid ""
"First, the try-except code block in the main server loop will detect if "
"the error is an ``OSError``. If it is, the main loop will exit directly."
msgstr "首先，主伺服器循環中的 try 和 except 程式碼區塊將偵測錯誤是否為「OSError」。如果是，主循環將直接退出。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:117 527c9ea4b40c48d786e37ae38639b643
msgid ""
"Secondly, if the error is from the network socket, it will first output the "
"error message and also stop the server by calling the function `stop`. And "
"the stop function has been defined as:"
msgstr "其次，如果錯誤來自網路套接字，它會先輸出錯誤訊息，並透過呼叫函數「stop」來停止伺服器。停止函數定義為："

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:126 3c1ddc7066fe478fb72fe0440ac29069
msgid ""
"For the stop tcp server function, it first set the ``self.running`` variable"
" to False, for stop the main loop of the server. After that, it calls the "
"`free_port` function to free the port which has been allocated. And the "
"`free_port` has been defined as:"
msgstr ""
"對於停止 tcp 伺服器功能，它首先將 self.running 變數設為 "
"False，以停止伺服器的主循環。之後，它會呼叫“free_port”函數來釋放已指派的連接埠。 `free_port` 被定義為："

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:137 0be2c10e6bd94c669310ff02fb804b29
msgid ""
"*Note: For more details of the `free_port` function, see the :ref:`tcp-"
"server-port-allocation-api` section.*"
msgstr ""
"*注意：有關 `free_port` 函數的更多詳細信息，請參閱 :ref:`tcp-server-port-allocation-api` 部分。 *"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:140 2d161cae990b4bd8a0e7f76f6ae54e93
msgid ""
"At the end of the operations, the TCP server closes all client sockets stored in the"
"self.clients dictionary and also closes the server socket."
"of clients which are accounted in the dictionary variable ``self.clients`` "
"and also close the server socket."
msgstr "在操作結束時，TCP伺服器將關閉字典變數「self.clients」中記錄的所有客戶端套接字，並關閉伺服器套接字。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:144 8d9d72393f2c4d04b54a82b0e9ecb465
msgid ""
"*Note: The ``self.clients`` variable is a dictionary that maps client "
"address tuples to an info dictionary. The key is the client address tuple "
"(``(ip, port)``) and the value is a dictionary containing connection details"
" such as ``'socket'``, ``'address'``, ``'id'``, and ``'connected_time'``. "
"See the example below which shows how entries are stored.*"
msgstr ""
"*注意：「self.clients」變數是一個字典，它將客戶端位址元組對應到資訊字典。鍵是客戶端位址元組（``(ip, "
"port)``），值是包含連接詳細資訊的字典，例如``'socket'``、``'address'``、``'id'`` "
"和``'connected_time'``。請參閱下面的範例，其中顯示了條目的儲存方式。 *"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:166 31136cb6ca1441a8ad56bf613f047ec0
msgid "TCP Server handling information API"
msgstr "TCP伺服器處理資訊API"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:168 e0eb184f7fc74d638df934dd3b70a69d
msgid ""
"The server handling information API documents the core TCP server methods "
"that manage client sockets, receive raw data, and send messages."
msgstr "伺服器處理資訊 API 記錄了管理客戶端套接字、接收原始資料和發送訊息的核心 TCP 伺服器方法。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:180 caa9213378e14a5986804e4c09f272ec
msgid ""
"`handle_client` is the main per-client handler in ``TCP_Server_Base``. It is"
" invoked after a client connection is accepted and is responsible for:"
msgstr "`handle_client` 是 `TCP_Server_Base` 中主要的每個客戶端處理程序。它在客戶端連接被接受後被調用，並負責："

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:184 958c3272e38546309404822be5e43430
msgid ""
"adding the client entry into ``self.clients`` with socket, address, id, and "
"connected time"
msgstr "將客戶端條目新增至「self.clients」中，其中包含套接字、位址、id 和連接時間"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:185 b61e8c15a51a4fcd8aeedb87fb1206c1
msgid "printing connection information and current client count"
msgstr "列印連線資訊和當前客戶端計數"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:186 499853560e7c49fab4d3f4970e0836f8
msgid "sending a welcome message to the client"
msgstr "向客戶發送歡迎訊息"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:187 480ca8697764498fb3b60bbad9672968
msgid ""
"broadcasting ``/client_alloc_port_range`` information to all clients "
"depending on port allocation mode"
msgstr "根據連接埠分配模式向所有客戶端廣播“/client_alloc_port_range”訊息"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:189 d4f6ec581f71479f9accfc8e6ddfb44f
msgid ""
"*Note: You can specify the port allocation mode in the arguments which has "
"been defined in the ``TCP_Server_Base`` class. The args which you can change"
" are ``port_add_step``, ``port_range_num`` and ``is_hand_alloc_port``.*"
msgstr ""
"*注意：您可以在「TCP_Server_Base」類別中定義的參數中指定連接埠分配模式。您可以變更的參數是“port_add_step”、“port_range_num”和“is_hand_alloc_port”。"
" *"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:195 3332e60134c144818cbad9ee9670f3c9
msgid "receiving raw bytes from the socket using `receive_message`"
msgstr "使用“receive_message”從套接字接收原始位元組"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:196 ffc19de5f2e6448f8dfa86382b72ea59
msgid "buffering incoming data until newline-terminated messages are complete"
msgstr "緩衝傳入數據，直到換行符終止的訊息完成"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:197 5599c38881f743b2b285a43b57f80dba
msgid "splitting and processing each message line-by-line"
msgstr "逐行拆分並處理每個訊息"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:198 4379426aed934a63ab888013c00c22e9
msgid "routing special commands beginning with ``/`` to `handle_command`"
msgstr "將以 ``/`` 開頭的特殊命令路由到 `handle_command`"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:200 d2d782beecec4cd08c03aaa7200c92e9
msgid "The `handle_command` function is defined as:"
msgstr "“handle_command”函數定義為："

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:211 0e5be543d51b47c4b3d278ee1895e6e3
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"In `handle_command`, there are variable conditional branches to handle "
"built-in commands like ``/help``, ``/time``, ``/clients``, ``/quit``, and "
"some file transfer commands. If you already added more commands by the "
"command extension API, the function will determine if the input message "
"matches the extension commands."
msgstr ""
"在「handle_command」中，有可變條件分支來處理內建指令，如「/help」、「/time」、「/clients」、「/quit」以及一些檔案傳輸指令。如果您已經透過命令擴充"
" API 新增了更多命令，則函數將確定輸入的訊息是否與擴充命令相符。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:219 5ec550e3acd6437faf76d3e4aa8d416c
msgid ""
"*Note: For more details of the command extension API and the built-in "
"commands, see the :ref:`tcp-server-command-api` section.*"
msgstr "*注意：有關命令擴展 API 和內建命令的更多詳細信息，請參閱 :ref:`tcp-server-command-api` 部分。 *"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:222 4973d45b4a6843c5a4f293cfd00d9075
msgid "logging normal chat messages and acknowledging receipt"
msgstr "記錄正常聊天訊息並確認收到"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:223 fd86dd8af215423baa10cd23496f4dd8
msgid ""
"removing the client from ``self.clients`` and closing the socket when the "
"client disconnects or an error occurs"
msgstr "從“self.clients”中刪除客戶端，並在客戶端斷開連接或發生錯誤時關閉套接字"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:233 d86a2ca1f2f54a2683d2bee076a5ee17
msgid ""
"`receive_message` is a thin wrapper around socket receive operations. It "
"reads up to ``msg_length`` bytes from the given ``client_socket`` and "
"returns the raw byte payload. Message decoding and newline message framing "
"are handled by the caller."
msgstr ""
"`receive_message` "
"是套接字接收操作的一個薄包裝器。它從給定的“client_socket”讀取最多“msg_length”位元組並返回原始位元組有效負載。訊息解碼和換行訊息幀由呼叫者處理。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:248 ee8e9bc8f0c24169a41913335c71e20f
msgid ""
"`send_message` sends data back to a specific connected client. It verifies "
"the server is running and the socket is valid, then:"
msgstr "`send_message` 將資料傳回特定的連線客戶端。它驗證伺服器正在運行並且套接字有效，然後："

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:251 6bc8f2ed0c5b47ebae081500b4a8ee17
msgid "accepts both ``str`` and ``bytes`` message payloads"
msgstr "接受“str”和“bytes”訊息負載"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:252 e8f911020564467da472399e31903bfc
msgid "trims string payloads and appends a newline if missing"
msgstr "修剪字串有效負載並在遺失時附加換行符"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:253 5264ca94bf774560b1546814589ce14e
msgid "encodes string payloads as UTF-8"
msgstr "將字串有效負載編碼為 UTF-8"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:254 11fec3c3b8284477a1a186a65206010b
msgid "sends the complete message with ``client_socket.sendall(data)``"
msgstr "使用“client_socket.sendall(data)”發送完整訊息"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:255 6850283513d84335a3dd665a2a3b1aec
msgid ""
"returns ``True`` on success, otherwise logs the error and returns ``False``"
msgstr "成功時傳回“True”，否則記錄錯誤並傳回“False”"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:257 a6d009915c714d0b91b27de9ab341828
msgid ""
"And there are also some other functions which are used to send message in "
"bulk to the clients, such as the `broadcast` function and the "
"`send_msg_to_specific_client` function."
msgstr "還有一些其他函數用於向客戶端批量發送訊息，例如“broadcast”函數和“send_msg_to_specific_client”函數。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:270 b85e6f0b61eb4f388cc7c18c08d01c1d
msgid ""
"In `broadcast` function, it will send a message to all the clients which are"
" in the ``self.clients`` variable, also delete the clients which are already"
" disconnected from the server. And if the ``exclude_client`` parameter is "
"not ``None``, the server will exclude the client which is specified by the "
"``exclude_client`` parameter when sending the message."
msgstr ""
"在「broadcast」函數中，它將向「self.clients」變數中的所有用戶端發送訊息，並刪除已經與伺服器斷開連接的用戶端。如果“exclude_client”參數不是“None”，則伺服器在傳送訊息時將排除“exclude_client”參數指定的用戶端。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:285 9b6a44f792db4afea1a0910d14bdfa54
msgid ""
"The `send_msg_to_specific_client` function is used to send one or more "
"message to one or more specific clients by their client IDs. And the "
"``message`` args should be input a send message command."
msgstr ""
"`send_msg_to_specific_client` 函數用於透過客戶端 ID "
"向一個或多個特定客戶端發送一條或多個訊息。並且“message”參數應該輸入發送訊息命令。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:290 5c93a8b7df9c4ba592e31a8a7c5d7dad
msgid ""
"These methods form the server's client I/O loop and ensure reliable message "
"exchange for connected TCP clients."
msgstr "這些方法會形成伺服器的客戶端 I/O 循環，並確保連線的 TCP 用戶端進行可靠的訊息交換。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:297 fc06292f70904c668e628446b1338225
msgid "TCP Server command API"
msgstr "TCP 伺服器命令 API"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:299 ba0fa4e7318744b8b676846bf49e4859
msgid ""
"The server supports several built-in commands and a command extension API. "
"The main entry point is the `handle_command` method, which is invoked for "
"any message starting with ``/``."
msgstr "伺服器支援多個內建命令和命令擴展 API。主要入口點是「handle_command」方法，任何以「/」開頭的訊息都會呼叫該方法。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:304 b5777f13d35f4f26ae617247f91c26b0
msgid ""
"We support two solutions for command handling, one is input a command in the"
" console, and the other is receiving a command from other clients, and you "
"can also call the functions which are defined for the commands in the code."
msgstr "我們支援兩種命令處理方案，一種是在控制台輸入命令，另一種是從其他用戶端接收命令，您也可以呼叫程式碼中為命令定義的函數。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:310 55f3dddd875a4c9c8ae20b9136d46687
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"*Note: You can select the solution which you want to use by changing the "
"args of the `TCP_Server_Base` class, the arg is "
"``is_input_command_in_console``. ``True`` allows the server to input the "
"command in console, while ``False`` does not allow it.*"
msgstr ""
"*注意：您可以透過變更「TCP_Server_Base」類別的參數來選擇要使用的解決方案，該參數為「is_input_command_in_console」。"
" ``True`` 允許伺服器在控制台輸入指令，而``False`` 不允許。 *"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:317 ad8952a11a4947988db649c68b52a743
msgid "Built-in client commands include:"
msgstr "內建客戶端指令包括："

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:319 39ff77f126e1412d8406d435655743e1
msgid "``/help``: returns the available command list and usage hints."
msgstr "``/help``：傳回可用的指令清單和使用提示。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:320 78375e446e9d48f1958b500306d3c73c
msgid "``/time``: returns the current server time."
msgstr "``/time``：傳回目前伺服器時間。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:321 622d1d6fabab4e3c9871b3d9f231c352
msgid "``/clients``: returns the list of connected client IDs."
msgstr "``/clients``：傳回已連線的客戶端 ID 清單。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:322 10f588280ba8440681dc59a414e3af8a
msgid "``/quit``: returns a goodbye message and disconnects the client."
msgstr "``/quit``：傳回一條再見訊息並中斷客戶端連線。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:323 9be97d4482b24ae98c3d863f51128eea
msgid ""
"``/file <file_path> <client_id>``: starts a file transfer request from "
"client to server."
msgstr "``/file <file_path> <client_id>``：啟動從客戶端到伺服器的檔案傳輸請求。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:324 bebd16ce5960408ebfd51b440943241c
msgid ""
"``/file_folder <folder_path> <client_id>``: starts a folder transfer request"
" from client to server."
msgstr "``/file_folder <folder_path> <client_id>``：啟動從客戶端到伺服器的資料夾傳輸請求。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:325 56efc16c32234ab28bae72fc31310836
msgid ""
"``/server_file_transfer_port <port> <client_id>``: internal protocol message"
" used to coordinate file transfer ports."
msgstr "``/server_file_transfer_port <port> <client_id>``：用於協調檔案傳輸連接埠的內部協定訊息。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:327 2f2a9a9f4bb74954b2da2e5e4d9f9169
msgid ""
"In `handle_command`, the server will first check if the command matches any "
"built-in commands. If it does, the `handle_command` will call the functions "
"which are defined for the commands."
msgstr ""
"在`handle_command`中，伺服器將首先檢查該命令是否與任何內建命令相符。如果這樣做，「handle_command」將呼叫為命令定義的函數。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:332 d5c00491ac2343c597c6bad8a8398ecc
msgid ""
"If a command is not recognized by the built-in handler, `handle_command` "
"will check if it matches any registered custom commands from the command "
"extension API. If the command is already registered, the `handle_command` "
"will call the function defined for that command. The command extension API "
"is defined as:"
msgstr ""
"如果內建處理程序無法識別命令，「handle_command」將檢查它是否與命令擴充 API "
"中註冊的任何自訂命令相符。如果該命令已註冊，則「handle_command」將呼叫為該命令定義的函數。命令擴充 API 定義為："

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:350 996f9af0f74e4e3a91427fe3c5ab134e
msgid "The args of the `register_command` function are as follows:"
msgstr "`register_command` 函數的參數如下："

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:353 1cecc25c6761455dbace5be3acfd7a86
msgid "``command_name``: The name of the command to register."
msgstr "``command_name``：要註冊的命令的名稱。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:355 dcc654ebd8e442a8bdc84d7a10b6529c
msgid ""
"*Note: The ``command_name`` should start with a slash (e.g., "
"``/my_command``) to be recognized as a command.*"
msgstr "*注意：``command_name`` 應以斜線開頭（例如，``/my_command``）才能被辨識為指令。 *"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:358 318f344187d94270a1a4d72570885b0e
msgid "``handler``: The function to call when the command is received."
msgstr "``handler``：收到指令時呼叫的函數。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:360 b1975fd3ac9b4b1d881ec7e426bde717
msgid ""
"*Note: The ``handler`` function must have and only have three parameters "
"which are ``client_socket``, ``client_address``, and ``command``. "
"``client_socket`` will be accepted as the network socket object that sent the"
" command, ``client_address`` will be accepted as the address of the client "
"that sent the command, while the ``command`` parameter will contain the "
"actual command string.*"
msgstr ""
"*注意：「handler」函數必須且僅有三個參數，即「client_socket」、「client_address」和「command」。 "
"``client_socket`` 將被接受為發送命令的網路套接字對象，``client_address`` "
"將被接受為發送命令的客戶端的地址，而``command`` 參數將包含實際的命令字串。 *"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:368 41a12356235c4a84a313c89e9014dfd7
msgid "``where_to_run``: Specifies where the command should be executed."
msgstr "``where_to_run``：指定應執行指令的位置。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:369 dbd6f0bf76c24392a9a8c8881a242f37
msgid ""
"``run_in_thread``: A boolean indicating whether to run the command in a "
"separate thread."
msgstr "``run_in_thread``：一個布林值，指示是否在單獨的執行緒中執行指令。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:371 b01ae3ada1c24cd7893860085676d8ec
msgid ""
"This extension API allows server-side and console-side custom commands to be"
" registered dynamically. Valid values for ``where_to_run`` are "
"``\"server\"`` and ``\"client\"``. The ``\"server\"`` means the command will"
" be handled when a client sends the command, while the ``\"client\"`` means "
"the command will be handled when the server input the command in console."
msgstr ""
"此擴充 API 允許動態註冊伺服器端和控制台端自訂命令。 “where_to_run” 的有效值為「伺服器」和「客戶端」。 "
"「伺服器」表示當客戶端發送命令時將處理該命令，而「客戶端」表示當伺服器在控制台中輸入命令時將處理該命令。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:380 c6e04ec672f840a4b2825d247ea454b1
msgid ""
"*Note: It's true that the valid values for ``where_to_run`` are too strange,"
" but we still didn't find a better way to define that.*"
msgstr "*注意：確實，``where_to_run`` 的有效值太奇怪了，但我們沒有找到更好的方法來定義它。 *"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:384 c16f63a156b94fec815ca854db5582e5
msgid ""
"The ways to run the command will be different according to the args "
"``run_in_thread``. If ``run_in_thread`` is ``True``, the command handler "
"will be executed in a separate thread from the server's thread pool. If "
"``run_in_thread`` is ``False``, the command handler will be executed "
"synchronously in the main server thread."
msgstr ""
"根據參數“run_in_thread”，運行命令的方式會有所不同。如果“run_in_thread”為“True”，則命令處理程序將在伺服器執行緒池中的單獨執行緒中執行。如果“run_in_thread”為“False”，則命令處理程序將在主伺服器執行緒中同步執行。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:392 5bb8206ec18f4e30b041f59d8f01149b
msgid ""
"*Note: We store the registered commands in a list variable with two "
"dictionary in its inner layer, and the list variable is defined as "
"``self._custom_handlers`` which is initialized in the `__init__` method. The "
"command and its handler will be stored in the one of the dictionaries "
"according to the value of ``where_to_run``. For ``\"server\"``, it will be "
"stored in the first dictionary, otherwise in the second dictionary. And the "
"key of the dictionaries are all the command name, and the value is another "
"dictionary containing the handler function. And there is also another list "
"variable defined as ``self._custom_handler_threaded`` which initialized in "
"the `__init__` method, it contains all the commands that should be run in a "
"separate thread or not.*"
msgstr ""
"*注意：我們將註冊的命令儲存在一個列表變數中，該列表變數的內層有兩個字典，該列表變數定義為“self._custom_handlers”，在“__init__”方法中初始化。命令及其處理程序將根據“where_to_run”的值儲存在其中一個字典中。對於``“server”``，它將儲存在第一個字典中，否則儲存在第二個字典中。字典的鍵都是指令名，值是另一個包含處理函數的字典。還有另一個清單變數定義為“self._custom_handler_threaded”，它在“__init__”方法中初始化，它包含所有應該在單獨執行緒中執行或不執行的命令。"
" *"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:411 7c89b48e35294024ac14fbe88f8185c0
msgid ""
"After that, the command handler will be called according to the command "
"name, and run them by a command executor which is defined as:"
msgstr "之後，命令處理程序將根據命令名稱被調用，並由命令執行器運行它們，命令執行器定義為："

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:425 adad339fc05047dd81c3bd67171a6789
msgid ""
"In this executor function, there is a try-except code block to catch the"
" error when running the command handler. If there is an error when running "
"the command handler, the server will log the error message and also send the"
" error message back to the client if the command is from the client side. "
"And in the try code block, the command handler will be called with the "
"command arguments, and also the client socket and client address if the "
"command is from the client side."
msgstr ""
"在此執行器函數中，有一個 try 和 except "
"程式碼區塊來捕獲執行命令處理程序時的錯誤。如果執行命令處理程序時發生錯誤，伺服器將記錄錯誤訊息，如果命令來自用戶端，也會將錯誤訊息傳送回用戶端。在 "
"try 程式碼區塊中，將使用命令參數呼叫命令處理程序，如果命令來自客戶端，也會使用客戶端套接字和客戶端位址。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:435 310214b7550f4c098c28e4f100ef1382
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"If the command doesn't run in the thread, the command executor will be "
"called directly in the `handle_command` function. But if the command should "
"run in a separate thread, the command executor will be submitted to the "
"server's thread pool using the `submit_task` method, which is defined as:"
msgstr ""
"如果命令不在執行緒中執行，則命令執行器將直接在「handle_command」函數中呼叫。但是如果命令應該在單獨的執行緒中運行，則命令執行器將使用「submit_task」方法提交到伺服器的執行緒池，該方法定義為："

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:450 4f8e669268de4c1995128b1a5bc222cf
msgid ""
"The `submit_task` method is a helper function that submits a callable to the"
" server's internal thread pool executor. It accepts a function and its "
"arguments, and schedules it for execution in a separate thread. This allows "
"long-running or blocking command handlers to run without blocking the main "
"server loop."
msgstr ""
"「submit_task」方法是一個輔助函數，它將可呼叫函數提交給伺服器的內部執行緒池執行器。它接受一個函數及其參數，並安排它在單獨的線程中執行。這允許長時間運行或阻塞命令處理程序運行而不會阻塞主伺服器循環。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:457 ca419b79f5ee4a70bf4bb9da3b99b6d5
msgid ""
"As a high level TCP network protocol, A temporary TCP server and a client "
"can also be created very simply. The temporary TCP server or client can be "
"used for scenarios that functions which need other sockets or ports for avoid to "
"have a conflict with the main server or client loop. For example, file "
