#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:491 682feeccb237422984cfe829eb5c6e47
msgid "``/stop``: stops the server and closes all active connections."
msgstr "``/stop``：停止伺服器並關閉所有活動連線。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:492 7faacc60383b4bd8ae73abfa19246238
msgid "``/status``: prints the current connection count and running state."
