#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:496 0ef5aed4f7394d4aad9114a638940911
msgid ""
"``/file_folder <folder_path> <client_id>``: sends a folder from the server "
"to a specific client."
msgstr "``/file_folder <folder_path> <client_id>``：將資料夾從伺服器傳送到特定客戶端。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:497 0f1f7a88823d4b1db348a242bf91b718
msgid ""
"``/multiple_file_multiple_client <file1> <file2> ... <client1> <client2> "
