#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:573 f176a36916364c9ca6dd78d8246226bc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"We recommend that if you want to use the mono-file transfer function, "
"use the `file_transfer_server_recv_client_start_thread` function first, "
"unless the functions which called the mono-file transfer function are "
"already in a separate thread, then you can call the "
"`file_transfer_server_recv_client_start` function directly, or the file "
"transfer functions are may not be very stable. And for the other file "
"transfer functions, we don't strongly recommend you to use them in threads, "
"because there are already some thread control mechanisms in the functions, "
"so don't worry about the concurrency. And if you call them in "
"threads, there may be some unexpected errors and also unnecessary "
"complexity."
msgstr ""
"我們建議您如果要使用單一檔案傳輸函數，請先使用 file_transfer_server_recv_client_start_thread "
"函數，除非呼叫單一檔案傳輸函數的函數已經在單獨的執行緒中，那麼您可以直接呼叫 "
"file_transfer_server_recv_client_start "
"函數，否則檔案傳輸函數可能不太穩定。而對於其他檔案傳輸函數，我們不太建議您在線程中使用它們，因為函數中已經有一些線程控制機制，所以不必擔心並發效能。如果你在執行緒中呼叫它們，可能會出現一些意想不到的錯誤，而且也可能會變得不必要的複雜性。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:587 8d5b255ca29042509aad566d071c2c58
msgid ""
"*Note: The file transfer API functions are designed to be called from the "
"command handlers for both client-initiated and server-initiated transfers. "
"They handle the coordination of transfer ports, client connections, and the "
"actual file data transfer operations.*"
msgstr ""
"*注意：文件傳輸 API 函數設計為從命令處理程序調用，以進行客戶端啟動和伺服器啟動的傳輸。它們處理傳輸連接埠、客戶端連接和實際檔案資料傳輸操作的協調。"
" *"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:593 e267899fa3654422bf36e82e026c0f69
msgid "Client-to-server transfer flow:"
msgstr "客戶端到伺服器的傳輸流程："

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:595 dafc23a2cbc94d29adcba6e27c575daf
msgid "The client sends ``/file`` or ``/file_folder`` to request a transfer."
msgstr "客戶端發送``/file`` 或``/file_folder`` 來請求傳輸。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:597 c82cac6540f445b9a8e8fe1d898958a3
msgid ""
"``handle_command`` starts a dedicated file-server thread using "
"``file_transfer_server_recv_server_start_thread``."
msgstr ""
"「handle_command」使用「file_transfer_server_recv_server_start_thread」啟動專用檔案伺服器執行緒。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:599 0fb4e13e2f9a4c4f982abff5ce812d75
msgid ""
"The server allocates an ephemeral transfer port with ``palloc`` and sends "
"``/server_file_transfer_port <port> <client_id>`` back to the client."
msgstr ""
"伺服器使用“palloc”分配臨時傳輸連接埠並將“/server_file_transfer_port <port> "
"<client_id>”傳回客戶端。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:603 66c6621aa97542b49c81ea27f0bc4267
msgid ""
"The client connects to that transfer port and sends file metadata, including"
" length-prefixed filename and file size."
msgstr "用戶端連接到該傳輸連接埠並發送文件元數據，包括帶有長度前綴的檔案名稱和檔案大小。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:606 7571fffe513045eaa747dc1b2d2876cc
msgid "The server receives the file and writes it under ``received_files``."
msgstr "伺服器接收檔案並將其寫入“received_files”下。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:609 5bbe70007f10457890789d86bc17b4c1
msgid "Server-to-client transfer flow:"
msgstr "伺服器到客戶端的傳輸流程："

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:611 2a6a841109fc492d8308c012ae74c1fe
msgid ""
"``file_transfer_server_recv_client_start`` is used to initiate outgoing "
"transfers from server to a connected client."
msgstr "``file_transfer_server_recv_client_start`` 用於啟動從伺服器到連線的客戶端的傳出傳輸。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:613 e432fc7c6d80453da278dacde19cabab
msgid ""
"The server sends transfer commands to the client socket and waits for the "
"client to establish the file transfer connection."
msgstr "伺服器向客戶端套接字發送傳輸命令，並等待客戶端建立檔案傳輸連線。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:615 fe161c64ff2e4c53b7ce7e60589e3a24
msgid ""
"Folder transfers are performed recursively, with each file transfer "
"respecting ``self.max_file_transfer_thread_num`` and the configured "
"semaphore limit."
msgstr "資料夾傳輸以遞歸方式執行，每個檔案傳輸都遵循“self.max_file_transfer_thread_num”和配置的信號量限制。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:618 78c1e3f118574ccba8be241f9ee69dc4
msgid "Common file transfer helper methods include:"
msgstr "常見的文件傳輸幫助方法包括："

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:620 f9f1a987d43f49898a9e10e1db1f6f77
msgid ""
"``file_transfer_server_recv_server_start``: receives file data from a "
"client."
msgstr "``file_transfer_server_recv_server_start``：從客戶端接收檔案資料。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:621 0ee6e0a2d46e443591c8804f9d075576
msgid ""
"``file_transfer_server_recv_client_start``: sends a file or folder to a "
"client."
msgstr "``file_transfer_server_recv_client_start``：將檔案或資料夾傳送到客戶端。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:622 6eb9f641886740e6a0115b15d5a9cc61
msgid ""
"``file_transfer_mode``: performs the low-level client-side transfer "
"handshake."
msgstr "``file_transfer_mode``：執行低階客戶端傳輸握手。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:623 346b9f84a1a744478abea5beb22dd2d3
msgid ""
"``file_transfer_mode_recv``: performs the low-level receive-side transfer "
"handshake."
msgstr "``file_transfer_mode_recv``：執行低階接收端傳輸握手。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:628 d03bc27c716645e5a375244673b67e22
msgid "Port allocation API"
msgstr "連接埠分配API"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:630 a35924ac9bb34a308b1ff0edac57bd92
msgid ""
"The server allocation APIs allow you to allocate a new port for another "
"servers. There are two kinds of port allocation modes."
msgstr "伺服器分配 API 允許您為其他伺服器指派新連接埠。連接埠分配方式有兩種。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:634 c74252dd96b44f1db6b982a5b9888874
msgid ""
"To change the port allocation mode, you can set the args "
"``is_hand_alloc_port`` in the server instance class. When input ``False``, "
"the server instance will choose the automatic port allocation mode, or "
"input ``False`` it will choose the manual allocation mode."
msgstr ""
"若要變更連接埠指派模式，您可以在伺服器實例類別中設定參數「is_hand_alloc_port」。當輸入“False”時，伺服器實例將選擇自動連接埠分配模式，或輸入“False”時，伺服器實例將選擇手動分配模式。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:640 7aa3d163bf354e95931c7574b34fc6ba
msgid ""
"We strongly recommend you that to use the automatic port allocation mode, "
"which is the default mode of the server, because the automatic port "
"allocation mode is simpler and also more stable than the manual port "
"allocation mode. In this mode, when calling the allocation APIs, it will "
"return ``0``."
msgstr ""
"我們最推薦您使用自動連接埠分配模式，這是伺服器的預設模式，因為自動連接埠分配模式比手動連接埠分配模式更簡單，也更穩定。在此模式下，呼叫分配API時，將傳回``0``。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:647 67b8c95463ac4d6ea023a2e7d15c6696
msgid ""
"*Note: The `bind` function in standard lib `socket` of the python executor, "
"when input ``0`` to the port parameter, will automatically assign an "
"available port by operating system.*"
msgstr ""
"*注意：python執行器的標準lib `socket`中的`bind`函數，當連接埠參數輸入``0`時，作業系統會自動分配一個可用的連接埠。 *"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:652 d18afcec308b4807a16019d98e92165e
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The other port allocation mode is the manual port allocation mode, there is "
"a port allocation range for the server. Please avoid opening other servers "
"in the same host, because in the existing version, the port allocation range"
" will be conflicted and some unexpected errors may be caused."
msgstr ""
"另一種連接埠分配方式是手動連接埠分配方式，伺服器有一個連接埠分配範圍。請避免在同一台主機上開啟其他伺服器，因為在現有版本中，連接埠分配範圍會發生衝突，並可能導致一些意外錯誤。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:659 c49291ef0a1b4dcb83297450887242aa
msgid ""
"The range of the port allocation is configured in the server settings. The "
"minimum allocatable port is ``self.port-"
"self.port_add_step*self.port_range_num``, and the maximum allocatable port "
"is ``self.port+1+self.port_add_step*self.port_range_num``."
msgstr ""
"連接埠分配的範圍在伺服器設定中配置。最小可分配連接埠為“self.port-"
"self.port_add_step*self.port_range_num”，最大可指派連接埠為“self.port+1+self.port_add_step*self.port_range_num”。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:665 0e9ecf5c00754955855f07a88e56410e
msgid ""
"*Note: The ``self.port`` is the args ``port`` of the server class. The "
"``self.port_add_step`` is the args ``port_add_step`` of the server class. "
"And the ``self.port_range_num`` is the args ``port_range_num`` of the server"
" class also.*"
msgstr ""
"*注意：「self.port」是伺服器類別的參數「port」。 "
"「self.port_add_step」是伺服器類別的參數「port_add_step」。而「self.port_range_num」也是伺服器類別的參數「port_range_num」。"
" *"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:671 3b99f158118341ffaaa6716669fc5703
msgid "There are some relevant methods that can be used:"
msgstr "有一些相關的方法可以使用："

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:678 8e9744f779214f81affafa1f446eaca4
msgid ""
"The `palloc` method allows you to get a port, When using this function, you "
"don't need to worry about the port allocation mode, because an allocation "
"mode detector is already implemented in this method."
msgstr "`palloc`方法允許你獲取一個端口，使用這個函數，你不需要擔心端口分配模式，因為這個方法中已經編寫了一個分配模式檢測器。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:690 b2a5f76b877b465980d6162e869921c4
msgid ""
"The `pfree` method allows you to free a port, the same as `palloc` method,"
" you don't need to care about the port allocation mode when using this "
"method."
msgstr "`pfree` 方法允許您釋放一個端口，與 `palloc` 方法相同，使用該方法時不需要關心端口分配模式。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:694 4058b14b49034f64a0c51e7a70f15de0
msgid ""
"And there are the main functions for you to call, and for more information "
"about the port allocation functions, see the :ref:`tcp-server-port-"
"allocation-api` section."
msgstr ""
"還有主要的函數供您調用，有關連接埠分配函數的更多信息，請參閱 :ref:`tcp-server-port-allocation-api` 部分。"

#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:698 385b478e6ab1489b84066e4f39e4b54a
msgid ""
"This mode is useful when you need an individual port for the server or  must "
"reserve a controlled range of ports for client-file transfers by manual port"
" allocation, such as in a testing environment or when multiple server "
"processes share the same host."
msgstr ""
"當您需要伺服器的單獨連接埠或必須透過手動連接埠指派為用戶端檔案傳輸保留受控連接埠範圍時（例如在測試環境中或多個伺服器進程共用相同主機時），此模式非常有用。"

